body.title: The Rise of Bukidnon Culture
body.description: This exhibit showcases the rich cultural heritage of Bukidnon, featuring traditional clothing, rituals, and ancestral practices that shaped the identity of the indigenous tribes across the province.

userAgent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/142.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/142.0.0.0

body.title: The Battle for Independence
body.description: A collection of artifacts, documents, and stories highlighting the struggles and victories of local heroes who fought for freedom during the colonial era in the Philippines.

userAgent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/142.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/142.0.0.0

body.title: Ancient Tools & Early Settlements
body.description: An exhibit displaying primitive tools, pottery, and early settlement remains that provide insight into how ancient communities lived, farmed, and adapted to the environment.

userAgent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/142.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/142.0.0.0

body.title: The Evolution of Philippine Currency
body.description: A timeline of the Philippine currency system, showcasing old coins, paper bills, and rare monetary artifacts used from pre-colonial trade up to the modern era.

userAgent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/142.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/142.0.0.0

body.title: Legends of the Mindanao Highlands
body.description: This exhibit highlights mythical stories and folklore passed down through generations, narrating the origin tales, heroes, and creatures believed to have roamed the highlands of Mindanao.
